We believe our commission software Securities ProStation® more than meets that objective. Your advisors can easily and quickly get answers 24/7/365 from anywhere. Compliance is an integral part of every securities firms business. Securities SurveillanceStation™ is an automated exception reporting system that was designed based on our staff’s compliance expertise. Today all three systems are used by small, medium and large broker dealers throughout the United States to maximize back office efficiency and minimize operational and compliance costs. The combined functionality of our products allows you to have a truly integrated suite of software to fully automate your business.
